# File Browser Flow
# Demonstrates: climp with no args, file browser navigation, selecting a file, brief playback, quit.

Output demo/browser.gif

Set Shell "powershell"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Margin 20
Set MarginFill "#FF8C00"
Set BorderRadius 10
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 100ms

Sleep 1s
Type "climp"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Down
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s
Up
Sleep 1s

Enter
Sleep 5s
Space
Sleep 1s
